<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset='utf-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Application Update - CS Guild</title>
    <style>
      @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap');

      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family:
          'Inter',
          -apple-system,
          BlinkMacSystemFont,
          'Segoe UI',
          Roboto,
          sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #ffffff;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0f23 0%, #1a1a2e 100%);
        padding: 16px;
        min-height: 100vh;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 100%);
        border-radius: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);
      }

      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444 0%, #dc2626 100%);
        padding: 24px 32px 20px;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .header::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(
          90deg,
          transparent 0%,
          rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 50%,
          transparent 100%
        );
        transform: translateX(-100%);
        animation: shine 3s ease-in-out infinite;
      }

      @keyframes shine {
        0% {
          transform: translateX(-100%);
        }
        50% {
          transform: translateX(100%);
        }
        100% {
          transform: translateX(100%);
        }
      }

      .logo {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #ffffff;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      }

      .logo::before {
        content: '</>';
        font-size: 20px;
        background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ffffff, #fecaca);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
      }

      .header h1 {
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 400;
        margin: 0;
        font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      }

      .header h1::before {
        content: '// ';
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
      }

      .content {
        padding: 32px;
      }

      .rejection-hero {
        background: linear-gradient(
          135deg,
          rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.15) 0%,
          rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.15) 100%
        );
        border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 32px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .rejection-hero::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        height: 2px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ef4444, #dc2626, #b91c1c, #ef4444);
        background-size: 300% 100%;
        animation: rejectionShift 3s ease infinite;
      }

      @keyframes rejectionShift {
        0%,
        100% {
          background-position: 0% 50%;
        }
        50% {
          background-position: 100% 50%;
        }
      }

      .rejection-icon {
        font-size: 64px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        display: block;
      }

      .rejection-title {
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: 700;
        background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ef4444, #dc2626, #b91c1c);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        line-height: 1.2;
      }

      .rejection-subtitle {
        font-size: 18px;
        color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.9);
        font-weight: 500;
        font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      }

      .greeting {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 500;
        color: #ffffff;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .description {
        font-size: 15px;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
        margin-bottom: 24px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .project-info {
        background: linear-gradient(
          135deg,
          rgba(31, 41, 55, 0.6) 0%,
          rgba(55, 65, 81, 0.6) 100%
        );
        border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 24px;
        margin: 24px 0;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      }

      .project-info::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        height: 2px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ef4444, #dc2626, #b91c1c, #ef4444);
        background-size: 300% 100%;
        animation: projectShift 4s ease infinite;
      }

      @keyframes projectShift {
        0%,
        100% {
          background-position: 0% 50%;
        }
        50% {
          background-position: 100% 50%;
        }
      }

      .project-info h3 {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #ffffff;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 6px;
      }

      .project-info h3::before {
        content: '📋';
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      .info-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
        gap: 16px;
      }

      .info-item {
        background: rgba(31, 41, 55, 0.5);
        border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 12px;
      }

      .info-label {
        font-size: 11px;
        font-weight: 500;
        color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.8);
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
        font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      }

      .info-value {
        font-size: 15px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #ffffff;
        word-break: break-word;
      }

      .message-section {
        background: linear-gradient(
          135deg,
          rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1) 0%,
          rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.1) 100%
        );
        border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 24px;
        margin: 24px 0;
      }

      .message-section h3 {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #ffffff;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
      }

      .message-section h3::before {
        content: '💬';
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      .message-content {
        background: rgba(31, 41, 55, 0.3);
        border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 16px;
        font-style: italic;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .encouragement-section {
        background: linear-gradient(
          135deg,
          rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1) 0%,
          rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.1) 100%
        );
        border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 24px;
        margin: 24px 0;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .encouragement-section h3 {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #ffffff;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }

      .encouragement-section p {
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6 0%, #a855f7 100%);
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 10px 28px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        border: 2px solid transparent;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }

      .cta-button:hover {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed 0%, #9333ea 100%);
        transform: translateY(-1px);
      }

      .footer {
        background: linear-gradient(
          135deg,
          rgba(31, 41, 55, 0.8) 0%,
          rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.8) 100%
        );
        padding: 24px 32px;
        text-align: center;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
      }

      .footer-brand {
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #ffffff;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
        font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      }

      .footer-brand::before {
        content: '// ';
        color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.8);
      }

      .footer-tagline {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }

      .footer-links {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .footer-link {
        color: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.8);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 500;
        transition: color 0.3s ease;
      }

      .footer-link:hover {
        color: #8b5cf6;
      }

      .footer-note {
        font-size: 11px;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .container {
          margin: 8px;
          border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .content {
          padding: 20px;
        }

        .rejection-hero {
          padding: 24px 16px;
        }

        .rejection-title {
          font-size: 22px;
        }

        .info-grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .footer-links {
          flex-direction: column;
          gap: 10px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <div class='header'>
        <div class='logo'>CS Guild</div>
        <h1>Project Application Update</h1>
      </div>

      <div class='content'>
        <div class='rejection-hero'>
          <span class='rejection-icon'>📝</span>
          <h2 class='rejection-title'>Application Not Selected</h2>
          <p class='rejection-subtitle'>Keep exploring opportunities</p>
        </div>

        <p class='greeting'>Hey {{firstName}},</p>

        <p class='description'>
          Thank you for your interest in joining
          <strong>{{projectName}}</strong>
          as a
          <strong>{{roleName}}</strong>. After careful consideration, we've decided not to move forward with your application at this time.
        </p>

        <div class='project-info'>
          <h3>Application Details</h3>
          <div class='info-grid'>
            <div class='info-item'>
              <div class='info-label'>Project</div>
              <div class='info-value'>{{projectName}}</div>
            </div>
            <div class='info-item'>
              <div class='info-label'>Applied Role</div>
              <div class='info-value'>{{roleName}}</div>
            </div>
            <div class='info-item'>
              <div class='info-label'>Decision</div>
              <div class='info-value' style="color: #ef4444;">❌ Not Selected</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {{#if reviewMessage}}
        <div class='message-section'>
          <h3>Feedback from Project Owner</h3>
          <div class='message-content'>
            "{{reviewMessage}}"
          </div>
        </div>
        {{/if}}

        <div class='encouragement-section'>
          <h3>Don't Give Up! 🚀</h3>
          <p>
            This decision doesn't reflect your abilities or potential. Keep building your skills, contributing to the community, and applying to projects that match your interests.
          </p>
          <a href='{{projectsUrl}}' class='cta-button'>Explore More Projects</a>
        </div>

        <p class='description'>
          <strong>Next Steps:</strong>
        </p>
        <ul style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8); margin-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 24px;">
          <li>Continue exploring other exciting projects in the community</li>
          <li>Build your skills and portfolio with personal projects</li>
          <li>Engage with the community through forums and events</li>
          <li>Consider starting your own project and recruiting team members</li>
        </ul>

        <p class='description'>
          Remember, every "no" brings you closer to the right opportunity. Keep pushing forward, and don't hesitate to reach out to our support team at
          {{supportEmail}}
          if you need guidance or have questions.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class='footer'>
        <div class='footer-brand'>Built with ❤️ by {{organizationName}}</div>
        <p class='footer-tagline'>Supporting your development journey</p>

        <div class='footer-links'>
          <a href='{{projectsUrl}}' class='footer-link'>Browse Projects</a>
          <a href='{{dashboardUrl}}' class='footer-link'>Dashboard</a>
        </div>

        <p class='footer-note'>
          console.log("Keep coding, keep growing! 💪");
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
